Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
defHierChar(25.10)                                          defHierChar(25.10)

Name
       defHierChar

Syntax
        defHierChar<delimiter>

       Type: String

       Default: /

       Specifies  the hierarchy delimiter character for the defOut and defOut-
       BySection commands. For example, to set / as  the  delimiter,  use  the
       following code:

       set defHierChar /

       Note:

              * You cannot unset this variable.

              * The defHierChar is for the defOut and defOutBySection commands
                only.  It does not change the hierarchy delimiter character of
                Innovus.

       The hierarchy delimiter used appears in the output DEF  File  as  shown
       below.

       DIVIDERCHAR "/" ;

Related Information
              * defOut

              * defOutBySection

